reviewText:
The first D.V.D. is of Elvis from 1954 thru 1960. It contains footage of Elvis in concert and on T.V. from those early years. Just great
material.
The second D.V.D. is mostly footage from "Aloha From Hawaii" which was a great telivised concert, but other sources were available
but not used.
I thought the first D.V.D. was much better than the second D.V.D. For a set I Likes it
